          <h2 data-gm-brief-title>当日养护简报</h2>
        </div>
        <span>AI 汇总 · 人工复核</span>
      </header>
      <p class="gm-brief-meta" data-gm-brief-meta>等待当前日期分析结果。</p>
      <div class="gm-brief-list" data-gm-brief>
