  <section class="gm-flow-band">
    <header>
      <div>
        <p class="gm-kicker">LANDSCAPE CHECKS</p>
        <h2>当前节点巡检项目</h2>
      </div>
      <p data-gm-project-summary>选择地图节点查看四类绿化指标</p>
    </header>
    <div class="gm-project-grid" data-gm-projects>
      <article data-project="trees"><span>乔木冠层</span><strong>待分析</strong><p>冠层密度、叶色和枝干状态</p></article>
      <article data-project="shrubs"><span>灌木绿篱</span><strong>待分析</strong><p>整齐度、长势和侵界迹象</p></article>
      <article data-project="groundcover"><span>草坪地被</span><strong>待分析</strong><p>覆盖状态、裸斑和枯黄迹象</p></article>
      <article data-project="issues"><span>异常复核</span><strong>待分析</strong><p>仅显示中高可信度问题</p></article>
